        <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
            <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
            <p>Papers include personal correspondence, 1896-1957; minutes of Local Assembly 300
                (window glass trades), Knights of Labor, Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania; unpublished
                history, by Slight of National Window Glass Workers Association of America;
                correspondence, minutes, ballots, tally sheets, 1901-1924; legal and financial
                papers, 1889-1921; Minutes of the Allied Building Trades (council) of Rochester, NY,
                1932-1954; wage scales and working rules, convention proceedings, pamphlets,
                periodicals clippings, and membership cards, chiefly of National Window Glass
                Workers.</p>
        </scopecontent>
